This jQuery plugin in currently in development.

Send me an email on http://www.vincentdieltiens.be/en/contact if you want to 
know when the first version is released or if you want to participate to the 
development.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This plugin makes HTML tables more flexible :
	- Some columns can be resized (without changing the table width)
	- The content of some cell can be truncated if it's too long for
	  the cell width.
	- 